// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0450 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 3bbdbcfb-c53d-54f6-9f1c-53f50c3da26d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:17.04*")
